Name: Credential Storage and Retrieval Tool
Description: A tool that stores or retrieves all credentials from a JSON file. Supports storing a new credential with a unique name and listing all stored credentials.
Param: action: The action to perform. Use "store" to save a credential or "retrieve_all" to fetch all credentials. ONE OF THESE IS REQURED either "store" or "retrieve_all"
Param: name: The name or identifier for the credential (only needed when storing).
Param: credential: The credential content (only needed when storing).

#!/usr/bin/env python3 ${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/store_credentials.py
